ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR ELECTRICAL SAFETY:

This software is designed to control electrical devices through relay modules.
The authors and contributors provide this software for educational and 
hobbyist purposes. Users are solely responsible for:

1. Ensuring proper electrical safety measures when working with AC/DC loads
2. Using appropriately rated components for their specific applications
3. Following local electrical codes and regulations
4. Obtaining proper electrical installation by qualified personnel for AC loads
5. Understanding the risks associated with electrical devices and relay control

The authors and contributors disclaim all liability for any electrical hazards,
property damage, personal injury, or other consequences arising from the use
of this software in electrical control applications.

USE AT YOUR OWN RISK. ELECTRICAL SAFETY IS YOUR RESPONSIBILITY.

