PROJECT INFORMATION:

Project: IoT Controlled Relay System
Version: 2.0.0
Platform: Raspberry Pi Pico W with MicroPython
Purpose: Professional WiFi relay controller with enterprise security features

Features:
- Secure web-based control interface
- Enterprise-grade security (authentication, rate limiting, CSRF protection)
- Modern responsive web design
- RESTful API with comprehensive documentation
- Safety mechanisms and fail-safe operation
- Real-time monitoring and statistics
- Professional logging and error handling

For more information, documentation, and support, please refer to the
README.md file and project documentation.
